included.groupDescription: This Group is intended to be an open forum for both clinicians and persons with lived experience around mental health to come together for mutual benefit; sharing ideas, news items, best practices, speaking gigs, book launches, speaking engagements, trainings, new research, and relevant employment opportunities.  We seek to educate the public and each other about mental illness, reduce stigma and advocate for the rights, dignity, and lives of the community of persons with mental illness.  **THIS GROUP DOES NOT SHARE GROUP MEMBER INFORMATION OR SEEK TO MONETIZE ITS MEMBERSHIP**

When former US President Barack Obama was asked to share his most important career advice for young people, he replied...

"Just learn how to get stuff done."

It's a simple yet powerful answer. You can talk about things all day, but the power lies not in what you say, but in what you do. 

(Via LinkedIn News)

Especialízate en el campo de la auditoría y adquiere los conocimientos para afrontar la dirección y realización de auditorías de empresas.

Primer día de EUROBIKE Show. 

Primer día de reencuentros con compañeros, amigos y gente maravillosa como Jesus Freire, Julia Werling, Christian Lust o, por supuesto, el gran Ulrich Müller Bosom en el stand de Riese & Müller GmbH. 

Si decimos que Eurobike es una fiesta, es por cosas como ésta. ¡Bicis alucinantes y un ambiente espectacular para recordarnos la suerte que tenemos de trabajar en este sector!

#VivaLaBicicleta #ciclismourbano #urbancycling #cyclinglife #bicicletas #ciclismo

Todas las ciudades son mejores desde una bici, y #Frankfurt no es ninguna excepción.

El jueves dimos un maravilloso paseo por la bonita ciudad alemana a lomos de decenas de Brompton. 

Esrá siendo una maravillosa feria EUROBIKE Show por momentos como este, por reencontrarnos con el fantástico equipo de Brompton Bicycle (enorme abrazo a Joe F.,
Callum Cartwright y compañía), conocer a gente tan simpática como Catherine Bedford  de Dashel Helmets Limited y, por supuesto, compartirlo todo con mi compañero/amigo/hermano Fernando Lozano de Frutos. Bueno, ¡y gracias también a la gran Rebecca Couto por gestionarlo!

¡Que Viva la Bici y que viva ver el mundo en bicicleta!

#ciclismourbano #urbancycling #cyclinglife #eurobike #Frankfurt

text.text:
Je serai au Salon Vélo PRODAYS à Paris pour vous présenter toutes les nouveautés de GOFLUO ! 🇫🇷✨
Du 2 au 4 juillet, découvrez nos vêtements réfléchissants fonctionnels et stylés. Rendez-vous hall 4 stand A12!

#GOFLUO #ProDaysParis #VêtementsRéfléchissants #Sécurité #Innovation #bodyglowers
So blessed to share this fantastic journey with the best team ever 👊🏻 Julie Vets Yinthe Toussaint Anouk Mampuya Veronika Vimpelova Julie Kockx Karen Pang Karolien Guldentops 💪🏻

* tired but happy (but tired)

As we’re wrapping up an incredible 5-day stint at EUROBIKE Show in Frankfurt, we can’t help but feel incredibly blessed with where we’re standing as a brand, and of course with the people that join(ed) us on our journey. It was an absolute delight connecting with so many new friends and reuniting with familiar faces (you know who you are!).

To top that off, our CEO, Julie Vets, and Export Manager, Aurélie Dehennin, had the privilege of speaking at the Women in Cycling breakfast, a networking event focused on fostering inclusivity and attractiveness for women in the cycling industry. Big thanks to Isabell Eberlein for spearheading this fantastic initiative.

Eurobike truly exemplifies the awesomeness of this industry and the people in it - and we couldn't be happier and more grateful to be a part of this.
A big shout-out to the exceptional organisation for yet another successful edition. 🙌 

Our most heard quotes this week: 

 * Is this really reflective?! 😱
 * Finally a brand that understands what we, as women, want.
 * I’ve never seen this before!
 * …and of course many other German expressions like gans toll, geil,.. which we still question.

This fair was a boost and a confirmation that we need to continue this journey. 
Not just with our bodyglowers, but with the full GOFLUO mindset: If fashion can meet function, why dress down when you can dress up?!

#Eurobike2023 #WomenInCycling #GOFLUO #bodyglower
